queries.name: 1.soda_postgres_container.sixpayment_velocity_payment.aggregation[0]
queries.sql:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*),
  COUNT(CASE WHEN "dag_load_timestamp" IS NULL THEN 1 END),
  COUNT(CASE WHEN "load_timestamp" IS NULL THEN 1 END),
  COUNT(CASE WHEN "settlingRefNo" IS NULL THEN 1 END),
  COUNT(CASE WHEN "productId" IS NULL THEN 1 END),
  COUNT(CASE WHEN "settlementDate" IS NULL THEN 1 END),
  COUNT(CASE WHEN "valueDate" IS NULL THEN 1 END),
  MIN("grossAmount"),
  MAX("commAmount") 
FROM ods.sixpayment_velocity_payment

queries.name: 2.soda_postgres_container.sixpayment_velocity_payment.duplicate_count
queries.sql:
WITH frequencies AS (
              SELECT COUNT(*) AS frequency
              FROM ods.sixpayment_velocity_payment
              WHERE "productId" IS NOT NULL 
AND "settlingRefNo" IS NOT NULL
              GROUP BY "productId", "settlingRefNo")
          SELECT COUNT(*)
          FROM frequencies
          WHERE frequency > 1

queries.name: 2.soda_postgres_container.sixpayment_velocity_payment.duplicate_count.failing_sql
queries.sql:
WITH frequencies AS (
              SELECT "productId", "settlingRefNo"
              FROM ods.sixpayment_velocity_payment
              WHERE "productId" IS NOT NULL 
AND "settlingRefNo" IS NOT NULL
              GROUP BY "productId", "settlingRefNo"
              HAVING COUNT(*) > 1)
          SELECT main.*
          FROM ods.sixpayment_velocity_payment main
          JOIN frequencies ON main."productId" = frequencies."productId" AND main."settlingRefNo" = frequencies."settlingRefNo"

queries.name: 2.soda_postgres_container.sixpayment_velocity_payment.duplicate_count.passing_sql
queries.sql:

              SELECT "productId", "settlingRefNo"
              FROM ods.sixpayment_velocity_payment
              WHERE "productId" IS NOT NULL 
AND "settlingRefNo" IS NOT NULL
              GROUP BY "productId", "settlingRefNo"
              HAVING COUNT(*) <= 1)
          SELECT main.*
          FROM ods.sixpayment_velocity_payment main
          JOIN frequencies ON main."productId" = frequencies."productId" AND main."settlingRefNo" = frequencies."settlingRefNo"
